title: The Cigar Authority Smokes Moscow City and Burt Sugar
itunes:title: The Cigar Authority Smokes Moscow City and Burt Sugar
description: The guys interview boxing analyst Anthony Pepe and try his new energy drink "Bean Town." They review the new Hammer and Sickle madoro "Moscow City" as well as Burt Sugar's new cigar. Plus, the chat about the "do's" and "don'ts" on your New Year's resolutions. It's time for the finer things in life.. It's time for The Cigar Authority!
